description:
This year's Tag Team Captains are Mistress Kara and Cheyenne Jewel. These two are already bitter rivals after Kara destroyed Cheyenne and beat her out of the welterweight division. Kara moved on to take on AND DEFEAT the champion, Isamar.
Today is the beginning of what is heating up to be a very rough and mean season of tag matches.

Sasha Princess BanksDaisy Ducati

The first match is Mona Wales vs. Sasha Princess Banks. Each round is individually score but then added up at the end to decide the winner. New faces; New Tricks. No Mercy! This is Sexual Submission in the Mission! Round 1.
title: March Madness: Sexual Submission in the Mission round 1
